General.Name: Imprimerie Chirat Société Anonyme
General.Description: Imprimerie Chirat Société Anonyme engages in the printing business in France. It prints catalogs, guides, directories and brochures, magazines and journals, books, and fine books for various sectors, including art/culture, industrial, professional, institutional, marketing, voyage, luxury, large schools, education, medical, scientific, photography, products, associative, and other. The company was founded in 1911 and is based in Saint-Just-la-Pendue, France.
